  <brief_title>Edwards Cardioband System ACTIVE Pivotal Clinical Trial (ACTIVE)</brief_title>
  <acronym>ACTIVE</acronym>
  <official_title>Annular ReduCtion for Transcatheter Treatment of Insufficient Mitral ValvE (ACTIVE): A Prospective, Multicenter, Randomized, Controlled Pivotal Trial to Assess Transcatheter Mitral Valve Repair With Edwards Cardioband System and GDMT vs GDMT Alone in Patients With FMR and Heart Failure</official_title>
